<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Microsoft Internet Security and Acceleration (ISA) Server 2004 Service Pack 3 (SP3)</Title><Description>ISA Server 2004 Service Pack 3 provides increased security, new troubleshooting  options and tools available directly from the ISA Server Management console, new diagnostic logging functionality, and enhanced log viewer and log filtering options for ISA Server 2004 Standard Edition and Enterprise Edition. In addition, this service pack adds support for publishing Microsoft Exchange Server 2007 with ISA Server 2004.</Description><UninstallNotes>On computers running Microsoft Windows Installer 3.0, you can uninstall the service pack using Add or Remove Programs in  Control Panel. To uninstall this service pack, Windows Installer 3.0 (http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=40389) must have been installed prior to the service pack installation.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=77501</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=77501</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>